name: ArbShib
additional_notices: No active trades are found for this coin. Please submit a ticket at %{link} if you think this is an error.

description.en:
What is the project about?
ArbSHIB is a veritable catalyst within the Arbitrum ecosystem. it's a platform that integrates Defi, NFT and AI to create value for the community.The group aim to collaborate with the community to develop a suite of powerful AI+Web3 products. The community will receive a fair distribution of tokens. From the community, give back to the community.

What makes your project unique?
Deployed on Arbitrum one, all tokens are airdropped to the community, and Integrate AI+WEB3+NFT.

History of your project.
Newly established

What’s next for your project?
AI NFT

What can your token be used for?
For the community.
